Class ContentTypeBasedRespConverter<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.apptik.comm.jus.converter.AbstractSmartResponseConverter<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - expected Type to convert to
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Converter<NetworkResponse,T>

    public class ContentTypeBasedRespConverter<T>
extends AbstractSmartResponseConverter<T>
    Converter Map which uses different Converter depending on the media type. This is particularly useful when we expect the the same java Type that can be received in different formats for example JSON, XML, protobuf etc.
